      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1616 - He (Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as)) was asked about a man who gave the Zakat of his wealth to someone he thought was needy, but later found out that the recipient was wealthy.\nImam (as) replied: \"It does not suffice for him (the obligation is not fulfilled).\""
        ]
